          <from>THE PREMIER</from>
          <p>THE PREMIER : Mr. Speaker, certainly the energy future not just of Nova Scotia and Newfoundland and Labrador but of the entire region, will be affected by the Lower Churchill project and then ultimately what will happen on the Upper Churchill and of course the expiry of the agreement between Hydro Quebec and Newfoundland.</p>
